1angijuruqtitsumavagit, ataniiq, unanngat qakitisimagavinga,
2ataniiq, guutiga, ikajuqtaujumanirngmut nilliagama,
3ataniiq, tarngnira iluvirngmit makitilauqpat;
4ataniq niqturutinik inngiqvigisiuk, ilitsi itjurngᓁttuqutaujusi,
5ninngaumaninga qilamimmarikuluk anigurngmat,
6ajurunniitsiarama, uqalauqpunga, “aulataunianngilanga.”
7ataniiq, quviagigavinga, qaqqaqutiga napatippat sanngijuulluni;
8ataniiq ilingnut nillialauqpunga;
9“sunamik pivaallirajaqpat tuqutauguma?
10ataniiq, tusalaurit, nikagilungalu;
11qiksaangnira mumikpat taanisirngnirngmut;
12niqturumallunga ilingnik niᐰttuungillunga.
